                                "issuer":  "TCEL",
                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: GV-016/GV-019 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "GV-001 Board quorum required | Preventive | Block decision if quorum not met | Critical | Corporate Secretary. GV-002 Conflict disclosure and recusal | Preventive | Require recusal before vote | Critical | General Counsel. GV-003 Authority validation | Preventive | Reject action outside delegated authority | Critical | Corporate Secretary. GV-004 Material evidence pack required | Evidence | Block decision if evidence incomplete | Critical | Corporate Secretary. GV-005 Dissent preserved | Governance | Block decision pack if dissent suppressed | Critical | CRO/AI Governance. GV-006 Risk review required | Preventive | Require CRO sign-off before Board vote | Critical | CRO. GV-007 Compliance/legal review required | Preventive | Require CCO/General Counsel sign-off | Critical | CCO/General Counsel. GV-008 Capital source/use documented | Evidence | Block approval if undocumented | Critical | CFO. GV-009 Policy approval authority | Preventive | Reject unauthorized policy activation | Critical | Board/CEO. GV-010 Policy exception expiry | Preventive | Auto-expire and require re-approval | High | Policy Owner. GV-011 KPI source and formula | Evidence | Reject KPI without documented source/formula | High | Data Governance. GV-012 OKR owner and period | Preventive | Reject OKR without owner/period | High | Strategy Office. GV-013 Initiative stage gate | Preventive | Block progression without gate approval | High | Initiative Owner. GV-014 Benefit realization review | Detective | Compare realized vs. projected benefit | High | Strategy Office. GV-015 Risk appetite Board approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved risk appetite change | Critical | Board/CRO. GV-016 AI voting boundary | Preventive | Deny AI voting or approval action | Critical | AI Governance. GV-017 Resolution version integrity | Evidence | Reject mutable resolution record | Critical | Corporate Secretary. GV-018 Board material access | Preventive | Deny unauthorized access to Board materials | Critical | Security. GV-019 Cross-tenant access denial | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. GV-020 Decision outcome tracking | Detective | Create follow-up task for material decisions | High | Decision Owner. GV-021 Executive self-approval restriction | Preventive | Reject self-approval | Critical | Board. GV-022 Delegation expiration | Preventive | Auto-expire delegated authority | High | Corporate Secretary. GV-023 Late material disclosure | Detective | Flag and require justification | High | Corporate Secretary. GV-024 Board pack freeze | Preventive | Version/freeze data at cut-off | Critical | Corporate Secretary. GV-025 AI recommendation expiry | Preventive | Block use of expired recommendation | High | Model Risk. GV-026 Minute approval before archive | Preventive | Block archival until approved | High | Corporate Secretary. GV-027 Resolution authority validation | Preventive | Reject resolution outside Board authority | Critical | Corporate Secretary. GV-028 Strategy version approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved strategy version | Critical | Board/CEO. GV-029 Policy supersession control | Preventive | Require explicit supersession record | High | Policy Owner. GV-030 Governance action escalation | Corrective | Escalate overdue governance action | High | Corporate Secretary."
                            }
